OL,3,CEx-minister helps Afghanistan inquiry
OL,4,Cbut says he 'won't betray'
OL,5,Cwhistleblowers
OL,7,FEx-veterans' minister Johnny Mercer
OL,8,Fhas "agreed to assist" the Afghanistan
OL,9,FInquiry - but maintains he will not
OL,10,Freveal the names of those who told him
OL,11,Fabout alleged special forces murders.
OL,13,FMr Mercer previously applied to
OL,14,Fwithold the identities of "multiple
OL,15,Fofficers" who told him about
OL,16,Fallegations of murder and a cover-ups
OL,17,Finvolving UK Special Forces.
