OL,5,Cwhistleblowers
OL,7,FHowever, the chairman of the
OL,8,FAfghanistan Inquiry refused the
OL,9,Fapplication - saying its job is to
OL,10,Festablish the truth about "grave
OL,11,Fallegations of multiple murders".
OL,13,FIn a previous order compelling Mr
OL,14,FMercer to hand over the names, the
OL,15,Finquiry chairman said the consequences
OL,16,Fof failing to comply without
OL,17,Freasonable excuse would be "a criminal
OL,18,Foffence punishable with imprisonment
OL,19,Fand/or a fine".
