OL,5,Cwhistleblowers
OL,7,F"The Inquiry team will be taking this
OL,8,Fforward.
OL,10,F"For the time being, the Chair will
OL,11,Fnot be taking further action in
OL,12,Frelation to the Section 21 Notice or
OL,13,Fmaking further comment."
OL,15,FPosting on X, Mr Mercer said he "notes
OL,16,Fthe judge's comments" but his position
OL,17,F"remains unchanged".
OL,19,F"I will always do all I can to assist
OL,20,Fthis important inquiry," he added.
